  description="Looking for knee replacement in Manikonda? Dr. Karthik Manchala is an experienced orthopaedic surgeon in Alkapur Township, Hyderabad 500089 specializing in total knee replacement surgery."
  keywords="knee replacement in manikonda, best knee replacement surgeon in manikonda, knee pain doctor manikonda, total knee replacement hyderabad, knee replacement cost hyderabad"
  canonicalUrl="/knee-replacement-manikonda"
  structuredData={pageStructuredData}
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <Header currentPath="/knee-replacement-manikonda" client:load />

    {/* Hero Section */}
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary/50 to-background section-padding">
      <div class="section-container text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">
          Knee Replacement in Manikonda
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Dr. Karthik Manchala offers advanced knee replacement surgery in Manikonda,
          Alkapur Township, Hyderabad 500089. With over 12 years of experience,
          he specializes in total knee replacement for arthritis and severe knee pain.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Content Section */}
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="section-container max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Best Knee Replacement Surgeon in Manikonda
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          If you are suffering from chronic knee pain, stiffness, or advanced arthritis,
          knee replacement surgery may be the most effective solution. At Dr. Karthik
          Manchala Ortho Clinic located at Rd Number 25, Alkapur Township, Manikonda,
          patients receive personalized care and advanced joint replacement treatment.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          When Do You Need Knee Replacement?
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-muted-foreground">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Severe knee arthritis not improving with medications
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Difficulty walking or climbing stairs
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Knee deformity or instability
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Advanced Knee Replacement Surgery in Hyderabad
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Using modern surgical techniques and high-quality implants, Dr. Karthik
          Manchala performs total knee replacement and partial knee replacement
          procedures. The goal is to relieve pain, restore mobility, and improve
          quality of life.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Why Choose Dr. Karthik Manchala?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          With 12+ years of orthopaedic experience, extensive joint replacement
          training, and a patient-first approach, Dr. Karthik Manchala is a trusted
          knee replacement surgeon in Manikonda serving patients from Alkapur Township,
          Puppalaguda, Narsingi, and surrounding Hyderabad areas.
        </p>

      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Booking */}
    <BookingForm client:load />

    <Footer client:load />
    <FloatingButtons client:load />
  </div>
</Layout>
